item.title: Little Baby - Too Late
item.dc:creator: Little_Baby
item.description:
That’s the thing, I’m bad at identifying genres… If it has a good sound or meaning and isn’t modern hip hop/rap, I’ll listen to it! It’s that there’s so many sub genres of electronic that I can’t identify which is which.

item.title: Little Baby - Too Late

item.description:
Putting the genre might help, I’ll be totally up front right now - I don’t listen to anything where the person hasn’t put a genre. Some genres I just am not interested in, I think many of us feel the same way.

Myself, if it’s drum and bass, electro, dub/brostep it’s an ASAP listen. But everyone has different tastes
